**Convert FCC Decant Oil â†’ Battery-Grade Hard Carbon for Na-ion Batteries**

A process optimization tool for producing hard carbon anode materials from refinery waste streams. Targets the "Goldilocks window" (d002 = 0.37-0.40 nm) for optimal sodium-ion battery performance.

![Dashboard Preview](docs/images/dashboard_preview.png)

