## ğŸ”¬ Model Details

### Property Predictors

| Property | Model | Key Dependencies |
|----------|-------|------------------|
| d002 | Linear regression | T, S, O, rate, time |
| Capacity | Gaussian peak | d002 (optimal at 0.385 nm) |
| ICE | Linear | BET surface area |
| BET | Process severity | T, rate |
| Yield | MCR correlation | MCR, aromatics, T |

### Validation Range
- Temperature: 900-1300Â°C
- Sulfur: 1-6 wt%
- Heating rate: 1-20Â°C/min
- Hold time: 0.5-4 hr

